dct_title_s: Rakuchū Rakugai machimachi kona taisei Kyō saiken ezu.
dct_description_sm: Mounted cover title. Wood block print. Oriented with north at the top. In Japanese. Relief shown pictorially. Includes distance chart. Includes text and legend pasted on upper left corner. 1 map: col.; 88 x 57 cm., folded in cover 21 x 16 cm.
